title: Paper Rings
description:
Taylor Swift adds another song to the wedding reception rotation! She says a lot in Paper Rings, but is there a subtle callback in that has been overlooked in that song? Plus, she’s bragging about getting her man but how did they even get to that point? Nick, Amy, Lacey and Ana do some super-sleuthing, and maybe some suggestive story-telling.. So that’s how that happened?!
What did we miss? What else should we cover? Let us know!
